Here is a special picture of the beautiful but extremely hot Arizona desert that I took in 2007, when I first decided that I wanted to pursue photography. The guy I was seeing at the time was a great photographer and he took me to Arizona for a few weeks to teach me how to use a "real" camera and how to take beautiful pictures. This was one of the first pictures I shot at the beggining of the first day on our trip.
